Ankle flexes help improve ankle mobility and strengthen the muscles in the lower leg. Sit in a chair with feet flat on the floor. Lift one foot off the ground and flex it upward toward your body. Lower with control. Repeat for 10-12 reps on each foot.

• Sit in a chair with feet flat on the floor.
• Lift one foot off the ground and flex it upward toward your body.
• Lower with control.
• Repeat for 10-12 reps on each foot.
